{"tid":92350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"PS4 PRO貨車撞限高桿 Sony：受損30多台且絕不販售","createTime":"2017-01-23T13:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T16:34:30.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce62114933dd9985ba990bb048c113484b207445","tid":92350,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:50:09.000Z","msg":"今日中午於台北電玩展會場外，《ET 遊戲雲》獨家揭露一台載運PS4 PRO的貨車撞上基隆路地下道的限高桿而導致車體變形，車內載運的PS4 PRO紙箱嚴重變形，由於PS4 PRO去年底推出後就造成玩家瘋搶，電玩展前三日的3000台更是吸引玩家徹夜排隊，因此這次車禍也受到不少玩家關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2295/e2295534.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2295%2Fe2295534.jpg&h=899fecbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSony於稍早接受《ET 遊戲雲》訪問時表示，車內受損的確認是PS4 PRO，總數約有30多台，主要為20多位拿了號碼牌但沒有來結帳的玩家所剩下的，另外有現場10台備品，提供現場販售機器有問題可及時更換。Sony並保證未來這些受損的產品不會拿到市面上販賣。車禍現場無人受傷，至於其餘賠償的相關責任還在釐清中。"},{"pid":"44d4cbdda39d76a88c5cfb671f545771b6671409","tid":92350,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2295/e2295502.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2295%2Fe2295502.jpg&h=767dd9f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://game.ettoday.net/article/854922.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgame.ettoday.net%2Farticle%2F854922.htm&d=iZ4i5QPyjiZkb3EFLGXVpksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=ee2fd3d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://game.ettoday.net/article/854922.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9afeae2c8139cc8a3dd050c466ef411c1e8f50f4","tid":92350,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533ec411eb559dd1cd6cc49477576fb2b0d28ea9","tid":92350,"uid":20554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD零件"},{"pid":"6a57d98aace3a32dfbdf8e391cb5fec230a0ef21","tid":92350,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:18:35.000Z","msg":"攞去淘寶放咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5d2a7df3d0cde8b562ba382ea470d8be0bdc8d","tid":92350,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}